name: Khabib Khays
headline: Frontend Developer
creator: False
bio:
Hello! I am a React/Next.js frontend developer with experience working in teams of various scales. My experience spans both small teams and large companies. Additionally, I have a background in DevOps, which enhances my understanding of the development and deployment processes from a broader perspective.

Technical Skills

• Programming Languages: JavaScript (React/Next.js), Vue, Svelte, Python, C/C++
• Tools and Technologies: Docker, Docker-Compose, CI/CD, Git, Linux
• Experience: Developing frontend solutions using React/Next.js and Vue, creating Telegram bots and server applications in Python, and working in DevOps.
• Education: Senior year at Innopolis University, majoring in Information Security.
• My GitHub: github.com/KhaysK

Interests and Hobbies

Beyond programming and development, my interests include football and airsoft, which offer me a way to relax and enjoy an active lifestyle. I am also deeply passionate about board and computer games, inspiring me to create engaging and fun user interfaces.
